          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1625.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, crumble the <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> into the pan </p>\n<p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 5 min or until golden and softened – these are your <strong>caramelised mushrooms</strong></p>\n<p>Tip: Try not to stir the mushrooms too often, as this will stop them from caramelising!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1625.-step-4-x200.jpg",
