            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1625.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped basil</strong> with the <strong>Dijon mustard</strong>, <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p>\n<p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>basil dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
